test_name: DSORTOT compared to DSPRSINF and DSSEASDY
short_desc: DSORTOT must equal the sum of DSPRSINF and DSSEASDY
full_desc: Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 Total score) must equal the sum of Q1a1. DSPRSINF (Personal information) and Q1b1. DSSEASDY (Season/Day)

test_name: DSSMTOT compared to DSSMIMM and DSSMDEL
short_desc: DSSMTOT must equal the sum of DSSMIMM and DSSMDEL
full_desc: Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score) must equal the sum of Q1c1. DSSMIMM (Shoebox memory - Immediate) and Q1c2. DSSMDEL (Shoebox memory - delayed)

test_name: DSMMTOT compared to DSMEMIMM and DSMEMDEL
short_desc: DSMMTOT must equal the sum of DSMEMIMM and DSMEMDEL
full_desc: Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score) must equal the sum of Q1d1. DSMEMIMM (Memory - Immediate) and Q1d2. DSMEMDEL (Memory - Delay)

test_name: DSAPTOT compared to DSAPINT and DSAPTRAN
short_desc: DSAPTOT must equal the sum of DSAPINT and DSAPTRAN
full_desc: Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - total score) must equal the sum of Q1e1. DSAPINT (Apraxia - intransitive) and Q1e2. DSAPTRAN (Apraxia - transitive)

test_name: DSLGTOT compared to DSLGNAM, DSLGREP, DSLGCOMP
short_desc: DSLGTOT must equal the sum of DSLGNAM, DSLGREP and DSLGCOMP
full_desc: Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - total score) must equal the sum of Q1f1. DSLGNAM (Language - Naming), Q1f2. DSLGREP (Language - repetitions) and Q1f3. DSLGCOMP (Language - comprehension)
test_logic: If DSLGTOT ne DSLGNAM + DSLGREP + DSLGCOMP

test_name: DSMSETT compared to DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT and DSKNWTT
short_desc: DSMSETT must equal the sum of DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT and DSKNWTT
full_desc: Q1i1. DSMSETT (DSMSE Total score) must equal the sum of Q1b2. DSORTOT (1b2 total Score), Q1c3. DSSMTOT (Shoebox memory - Total score), Q1d3. DSMMTOT (Memory - Total score), Q1e3. DSAPTOT (Apraxia - Total score), Q1f4. DSLGTOT (Language - Total score), Q1g2. DSVISTT (Visuospatial - Total score) and Q1h2. DSKNWTT (Knowledge of the examiner - Total score)
test_logic: If DSMSETT ne DSORTOT + DSSMTOT + DSMMTOT + DSAPTOT + DSLGTOT + DSVISTT + DSKNWTT
comp_vars: DSMSETT, DSORTOT, DSSMTOT, DSMMTOT, DSAPTOT, DSLGTOT, DSVISTT, DSKNWTT

test_name: DSCRTTFR compared to DSCRT1FR, DSCRT2FR, DSCRT3FR
short_desc: DSCRTTFR must equal the sum of DSCRT1FR, DSCRT2FR, DSCRT3FR
full_desc: Q2d13. DSCRTTFR (Free recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d1. DSCRT1FR (Test trial - Trial 1, free recall), Q2d5. DSCRT2FR (Test trial - Trial 2, free recall), Q2d9. DSCRT3FR (Test trial - Trial 3, free recall)
test_logic: If DSCRTTFR ne DSCRT1FR + DSCRT2FR + DSCRT3FR

test_logic: If DSCRTTIF ne DSCRT1IF + DSCRT2IF + DSCRT3IF

test_name: DSCRTTCR compared to DSCRT1CR, DSCRT2CR, DSCRT3CR

test_logic: If DSCRTTCR ne DSCRT1CR + DSCRT2CR + DSCRT3CR

test_name: DSCRTTIC compared to DSCRT1IC, DSCRT2IC, DSCRT3IC
short_desc: DSCRTTIC must equal the sum of DSCRT1IC, DSCRT2IC, DSCRT3IC
full_desc: Q2d16. DSCRTTIC (Intrusions to cued recall - total) must equal the sum of Q2d4. DSCRT1IC (Test trial - Trial 1, intrusions to cued recall), Q2d8. DSCRT2IC (Test trial - Trial 2, intrusions to cued recall), Q2d12. DSCRT3IC (Test trial - Trial 3, intrusions to cued recall)
